  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc5\u0db9 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1 \u0dc4\u0dad\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dc4\u0dd9\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dd0\u0dba 11\u0d9a\u0dca \u0da2\u0dbd\u0dba \u0db1\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Four areas in Colombo will have no water for 11 hours tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The National Water Supply and Water Transport Board says that water supply to four areas of Colombo will be suspended for 11 hours from 9:00 p.m. on Saturday (30) to 8:00 a.m. on Sunday (31) due to emergency repairs.",
        "The areas where water supply is suspended are Colombo 9, Colombo 10, Colombo 11 and Colombo 12.",
        "The board further states that the water supply is being suspended due to an essential upgrade of the transmission water pipe system by the Greater Colombo Water and Wastewater Management Improvement Investment Program.",
        "Expressing regret for the inconvenience caused to water consumers due to disconnection of water supply, the board requests the public to collect water temporarily."
      ],
